ActMotor Vehicle Transport Act
PrecisCONDITIONS OF CARRIAGE REGULATIONS which stipulate that the conditions of carriage and the limitations of liability applicable to an extra-provincial truck undertaking are those set out in the laws of the province in which the transport originates, or in the absence of such a provincial law, are those agreed to by the undertaking.
